                    <li>We cannot be liable for prohibited information which would be incedentially disclosed as part of a user profile or twitter status text. If any such prohibited information is found on our website, the articles containing such information will be removed, and the violating user will be permanently banned from this website. Aforementioned prohibited information includes but is not limited to the following list: Email addresses, passwords, addresses, phone numbers, confidential business information, confidential legal information, illicit sexual content, graphic content depicting violence, unsolicited marketing/advertisements.
